description: Petro USA, Inc. does not have significant operations. It intends to operate truck stops and travel centers in the United States, offering diesel fuel and gasoline, full service and fast-food restaurants, maintenance and repair service for trucks, and groceries and convenience goods, among other products and services. The company was founded in 1984 and is based in Liverpool, New York. Petro U.S.A. Inc. was a former subsidiary of Sea Alive Inc.
